      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要更多数据来确保通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lagarde-says-ecb-needs-more-data-to-reassure-it-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行需要进一步保证通胀率回升至 2% 的目标，然后才会进一步降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/lagarde-says-ecb-needs-more-data-to-reassure-it-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 20:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
